\begin_inset Formula $n_{v}(\vec{r})=\sum_{\alpha}z_{\alpha}\rho_{\alpha}(\vec{r})$
\end_inset

 is the charge density of solvent site 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

, which is the number density 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{\alpha}(\vec{r})$
\end_inset

