\begin_layout Standard
The electronic structure of solute in gas phase is determined by the Schrödinger
 equation
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
H_{0}\Psi_{\text{gas}}=E_{0}\Psi_{\text{gas}}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}$
